review_data.title: The best Burgers in town and beyond
review_data.content: Simply the best burgers I ever had. I tried every Burger and all are fantastic. The same applies to the fries. Moreover these burgers are also tasty if delivered, which is not too often the case with Burgers.

review_data.title: Super lecker!
review_data.content: Super leckerer Burger und Sweet Potato Fries! Unbedingt mit der Haussauce bestellen. Die Burgerbrötchen sind köstlich fluffig.
